# ONNX Runtime DLL staging dir for the Windows dynamic-ORT build (#137, Slice 1).
#
# These are large (~16 MB) MIT-licensed binaries staged at BUILD time by
# `scripts/prepare-ort-dylibs.mjs` (invoked from `tauri.conf.json`
# `beforeBuildCommand`/`beforeDevCommand`) and bundled next to the exe via
# `tauri.windows.conf.json` -> `bundle.resources`. They are version-locked to
# `ort = =2.0.0-rc.12` (ONNX Runtime >= 1.24) and must never be committed — keep
# them as reproducible build output so the pin can be bumped without git churn.
#
# Tracked: only this .gitignore, so the dir exists in a fresh clone (the bundle
# resource path resolves) while the DLLs stay out of version control.
*
!.gitignore
